Headline: Cape Cod diver left with a whale of a tale after a humpback spat him out - CNN
Text: By Evan Simko-Bednarski, CNNUpdated 0223 GMT (1023 HKT) June 12, 2021  (CNN)A Cape Cod lobster diver is safe Friday, following a fluke encounter with a humpback whale that nearly made him the leviathan's lunch.
